<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بِأَحْكَامِهِ، وَالتَّحَلِّي بِآدَابِهِ، عِشْتَ سَعِيداً، وَمُتَّ سَعِيداً حَمِيداً.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ابن الْقَيِّمِ رَحِمَهُ اللهُ تَعَالى:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هَذَا وَنَصْرُ الدِّينِ فَرْضٌ لازِمٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لا لِلْكِفَايَةِ بَلْ عَلَى الأَعْيَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>بِيَدٍ وَأَمَّا بِاللِّسَانِ فَإِنْ عَجَزْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>تَ فَبِالتَّوَجُّهِ وَالدُّعَا بِجِنَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مَا بَعْدَ ذَا وَاللهِ للإِيمَانِ حَبَّـ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>ـةُ خَرْدَلٍ يَا نَاصِرَ الإِيمَانِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>بِحَيَاةِ وَجْهِكَ خَيْرَ مَسْؤُولٍ بِهِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَبِنُورِ وَجْهِكَ يَا عَظِيمَ الشَّانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَبِحَقِّ نَعْمَتِكَ الَّتِي أَوْلَيْتَهَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مِنْ غَيْر مَا عِوَضٍ وَلا أَثْمَانِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَبِحَقِّ رَحْمَتِكَ الَّتِي وَسِعَتْ جَمِيـ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>ـعَ الْخَلْقِ مُحْسِنَهُمْ كَذَاكَ الْجَانِي<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَبِحَقِّ أَسْمَاءٍ لَكَ الْحُسْنَى مَعاً<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فِيهَا نُعُوتُ الْمَدْحِ لِلرَّحْمَنِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَبِحَقِّ حَمْدِكَ وَهُوَ حَمْدٌ وَاسِعُ الْـ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>أَكْوَانِ بِلْ أَضْعَافُ ذِي الأَكْوَانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَبِأَنَّكَ اللهُ الإِلَهُ الْحَقُّ مَعْـ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>ـبُودُ الْوَرَى مُتَقَدِّسٌ عَنْ ثَانِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>بَلْ كُلُّ مَعْبُودٍ سِوَاكَ فَبَاطِلٌ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>مِنْ دُونِ عَرْشِكَ لِلثَّرَى التَّحْتَانِي<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>